org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr

Class QueryBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jnosql.aphrodite.antlr.QueryBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, QueryListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AntlrDeleteQuerySupplier, AntlrGetQuerySupplier, AntlrInsertQuerySupplier, AntlrPutQuerySupplier, AntlrRemoveQuerySupplier, AntlrSelectQuerySupplier, AntlrUpdateQuerySupplier

    public class QueryBaseListener
extends Object
implements QueryListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of QueryListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
